（2006）。文化創意產業之智慧財產權管理與經營—以霹靂布袋戲為例。私立世新大學傳播管理學研究所碩士論文，臺北。表演藝術雜誌，2002：4葉玉珠（2006）。創造力教學—過去、現在與未來。臺北：心理。潘淑滿（2008）。質性研究：理論與應用。臺北：心理。畢恆達（2005）。教授為什麼沒告訴我—論文寫作的枕邊書。臺北：學富文化有限公司。蕭文文（2007）。兒童劇團產業經營策略研究—以紙風車劇團為例。私立華梵大學工業設計研究所碩士論文，臺北。董健、馬俊山（2008）。戲劇藝術的十五堂課。臺北：五南。蔡曉芬（1996）。台灣地區公立兒童劇團現況之研究。國立高雄師範大學教育學系碩士論文，高雄。蔡慈娥（2006）。自發展理論探討兒童戲劇之語言—以《粉墨人生》為例。國立臺南大學戲劇研究所碩士論文。臺南。二、英文部分Amabile.T.M.(1983).The social psychology of creativity. NY: Springer-Verlag.Amabile.T.M.(1996).Creativity in Context. Boulder, Colorado: West-view Press.Amabile.T.M.(1997) Entrepreneurial Creativity through motivational synergy. Journal of Creativity Bebavior,31(1),18-26.Barron,F.,＆Harrington,D.M.(1981). Creativity, intelligence, and personality. Annual Review of Psychology, 32,76-439.Csikszentmihalyi,M.(1988).Society, culture and person: A system view of creativity. In R.J. Sternberg(Ed.), The nature of creativity(pp.325-339). Cambridge University Press.Davis,J.H.,＆Behm,T.(1978).Terminology of drama/theatre with and for children:a redefinition.Children’s Theatre Review,27(1),10-11.Dean,A.,＆Carra,L.(1980).Fundamental of play directing(4th ed.).Virginia: Dixon Dena Press.Feist,G.J.(1999). The influence of personality on artistic and scientific creativity. In R.J. Sternberg, Handbook of creativity(pp.275-295).NY: Free Press.Finke,R.A,Ward,T.B.,＆Smith,S.M.(1992).Creative cognition: Theory, research, and applications. Cambridge, MA: MIT Press.Gardner,H.(1993).Creating minds. New York: Basic Books Press.Graham Wallas.(1926) The Art of Thought. NY: Harcourt Brace and world Press.Gruber,H.E.,＆Davis.,S.N.(1988). Inching our way up Mount Olympus: The envolving systems approach to creative thinking. In R.J. Sternberg(Eds.), The nature of creativity(pp.243-270).NY: Cambridge University Press.Guilford,J.P.(1950).Creativity. American Psychologist,5,444-454.Jackson,P.,＆Messick,S.(1965). The person, the product and the response: Conceptual problems in the assessment of creativity. Journal of Personality,33,309-329.John.Ahart (2001)